{"tid":1474020,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[圍個爐取下暖] 想自殺手足入！","createTime":"2019-08-15T04:35:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T05:09:39.000Z","uid":57476,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c2f8f88ff79c7cfa3cff88118d6ddee003914312","tid":1474020,"uid":57476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:35:21.000Z","msg":"我唔知有幾多巴絲同我一樣 一直有自殺傾向 有問題只係想用自殘自殺解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但最近 每次當我一諗死亡 我就諗<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">少咗我一個 香港可能會輸架 我唔可以扔低大家</span></span><br />\n我知唔只我一個咁諗架 因為香港人真係好善良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我決定圍爐取下暖 希望留啲正能量係連登做一個小小嘅避難所 唔理你係和理非勇武(狗死撚開) 唔好理乜撚中計唔撚中計互屌 不如係度一人留句正面野 支持大家向前行好冇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有日我地會喺煲底除罩相見架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />約定你地"},{"pid":"5df78d41310af180ec109e90bc509cd00538b548","tid":1474020,"uid":57476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:38:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8456c4e395daaca3842316be0160b7956ec10d1","tid":1474020,"uid":57476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:38:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0d70f1cc92836c85299c06bc397fc17c59b2bb3","tid":1474020,"uid":57476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:39:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84623075cde76cc86420840dff3ac7f8fc6bd267","tid":1474020,"uid":1495,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:40:11.000Z","msg":"我哋約好要成功後喺煲底除口罩相擁"},{"pid":"ddf7710b93befa0b59a5f55fdd1bb89b69411876","tid":1474020,"uid":57476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84623075cde76cc86420840dff3ac7f8fc6bd267","tid":1474020,"uid":14